---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Ecosystem - Neurodiagnoses">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center">The Neurodiagnoses Ecosystem</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-slate-600 text-center">An AI-powered, open-source platform designed to integrate multi-modal data and enhance the diagnostic precision, risk assessment, and prognostic understanding of complex neurodegenerative diseases (NDDs).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">A Tridimensional Diagnostic Framework</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">Our system moves beyond static labels by organizing all patient data along three fundamental axes, providing a holistic and mechanistic view of the disease.</p>
        <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Axis 1: Etiology (The Why)</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Focuses on the root cause or predisposition, including genetic factors (monogenic or risk alleles) and significant environmental or infectious contributors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Axis 2: Molecular Pathology (The Plot)</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Describes the underlying biological processes, integrating multi-omics data to profile active pathological pathways like amyloid, tau, and neuroinflammation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Axis 3: Phenotype (The How & Where)</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Captures the observable manifestation, correlating clinical symptoms with their neuroanatomical findings from imaging.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 bg-light p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">The Dual-Output Engine</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">The Bayesian inference engine generates a comprehensive "Neurodegenerative Signature" for each patient, composed of two key parts:</p>
        <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div >
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">1. Classical Differential Diagnosis</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600">A familiar, ranked list of classical neurodegenerative diseases, each with a calculated posterior probability, enabling direct clinical interpretation.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">2. Tridimensional Annotation</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600">A rich, structured report detailing the patient's unique profile across the three axes, providing deep insight into the specific mechanisms at play for precision medicine.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>